    <item>
      <title>Moving soldiers</title>
      <link>https://wangjohn5507.github.io/project/project2/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Dec 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://wangjohn5507.github.io/project/project2/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;To familiar with algorithms including DFS, BFS, and UCS, the objective of the project was designing a simple GUI interface and simulated the movement strategy in League of Legends.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Alt text&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /project/project2/move_hu36e86e37c1757a4405f62bfd2d0a4ba9_194599_c9e1b4524f7fd7b14c33b7b9898ef616.webp 400w,
               /project/project2/move_hu36e86e37c1757a4405f62bfd2d0a4ba9_194599_b02d05511b5b3ac8f48694051a831ff1.webp 760w,
               /project/project2/move_hu36e86e37c1757a4405f62bfd2d0a4ba9_194599_1200x1200_fit_q75_h2_lanczos_3.webp 1200w&#34;
               src=&#34;https://wangjohn5507.github.io/project/project2/move_hu36e86e37c1757a4405f62bfd2d0a4ba9_194599_c9e1b4524f7fd7b14c33b7b9898ef616.webp&#34;
               width=&#34;494&#34;
               height=&#34;464&#34;
               loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;By entering different commands, the soldier will move to the destination without colliding with obstacles based on different path searching algorithms. This project totally divided into seven checkpoints to accomplish it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To download the project and know more details about the project, welcome to visit my &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/wangjohn5507/OOPII_Project&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Github&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
